    <!-- FAQ Questions and Answers -->
    <string name="faq_how_to_add_asset_question">How do I add a new asset to my inventory?</string>
    <string name="faq_how_to_add_asset_answer">To add a new asset, tap on the + button at the bottom of the home screen, then select \'Add Asset\'. Fill in the details of your asset including name, description, value, and other optional fields. You can also add photos of your asset by tapping on the camera icon.</string>
    <string name="faq_what_is_will_question">What is the Will/Inheritance feature?</string>
    <string name="faq_what_is_will_answer">The Will/Inheritance feature allows you to designate specific assets to be transferred to designated individuals in the event of your passing. This helps ensure your possessions are distributed according to your wishes. To use this feature, open an asset, tap on the \'Will Settings\' option, and select the intended recipient.</string>
    <string name="faq_how_to_sell_asset_question">How can I list an asset for sale?</string>
    <string name="faq_how_to_sell_asset_answer">To list an asset for sale, open the asset details page, tap on the menu in the top right corner, and select \'List for Sale\'. You can then set a price, add listing details, and choose visibility options. Once published, your asset will be visible to others in the marketplace section.</string>
    <string name="faq_how_to_transfer_asset_question">How do I transfer an asset to another user?</string>
    <string name="faq_how_to_transfer_asset_answer">To transfer an asset to another user, open the asset details page, tap on the menu in the top right corner, and select \'Transfer Asset\'. You can then enter the recipient\'s email address or username. The recipient will need to accept the transfer before the asset moves to their inventory.</string>
    <string name="faq_delete_account_question">How do I delete my account?</string>
    <string name="faq_delete_account_answer">To delete your account, go to Settings > Account Actions > Delete Account. Please note that this action is permanent and will delete all your data including assets, transactions, and personal information. Any assets that are part of pending transactions will be canceled.</string>
    <string name="faq_payment_methods_question">What payment methods are supported?</string>
    <string name="faq_payment_methods_answer">HyperPlux supports multiple payment methods including credit/debit cards, bank accounts, PayPal, and select cryptocurrencies. To add or manage your payment methods, go to Settings > Payment Methods. All transactions are secured with industry-standard encryption and security protocols.</string>

